 \sum_{i=1}^{n} \log(1 + d_{i}) \geq \sum_{i=1}^{n} \left( d_{i} - \frac{d_{i}^{2}}{1 + d_{i}} \right) = \mathbf{1}^{T} d - \sum_{i=1}^{n} \frac{d_{i}^{2}}{1 + d_{i}}. 
